data.description: This beautiful Florida pool home awaits you! This home has had numerous recent upgrades including: New roof, new screens installed on pool cage, updated kitchen with modern white shaker cabinets, stunning granite countertops and brand new kitchen appliances. New hurricane impact windows throughout the home, new hurricane impact automatic garage door, French doors, glass shower doors in bathrooms, tankless water heater, and SO much more! This home has been meticulously maintained and is perfect for those wanting to reside in the Country Club Corridor area in SE Cape Coral. This location provides convenient access to Veterans Bridge, numerous shopping and restaurant options nearby, close proximity to parks, and more! The backyard oasis boasts a salt water pool -solar heated, with ample room to unwind and relax, or for hosting guests. The well manicured yard and landscaping enclosed by a fence is perfect for little ones or pets to play. There was zero flooding/damage to this home with the past hurricanes, and best part: NO flood insurance required! No assessments! Don't let this great opportunity pass you by- Call today for your private showing!
